linkedin_data.headline: Chief Financial Officer at Mayo Clinic Health System
linkedin_data.summary:
Strategic and results-driven Senior Executive with extensive experience implementing efficient and cost-effective business practices that herald business transformations, maximize revenue growth, and strengthen company presence across large-scale healthcare environments. Proven track record designing and executing intuitive, comprehensive solutions that promote strategy development, process improvement, and quality assurance across multi-site medical operations. Action-oriented innovator able to optimize available financial resources while maintaining regulatory compliance and high-levels of HCAHPS and Core Measures scores. Noted leader and mentor adept at building and maintaining successful cross-functional departments. History of implementing large-scale business-development initiatives that re-engineer previously downturned healthcare frameworks and drive revenue growth and profitability. Demonstrated success spearheading acquisitions of numerous hospitals guaranteeing streamlined integration of operations. Award-winning professional continually recognized for service excellence, improving bad debt, and increasing margins. 

Areas of Expertise
Healthcare Management – Mergers and Acquisitions – Financial Management – Contract Negotiations – Process Improvement

Turnaround Strategies – Change Management – Regulatory Compliance – Recruiting – Relationship Management
